Example of panel to control the Turbo Energy inverter work mode system from home assistant

  - theme: Backend-selected
    title: Bateria
    path: bateria
    icon: mdi:battery
    badges: []
    cards:
      - type: entities
        entities:
          - entity: select.prog1_time
            name: Hora
          - entity: number.prog1_power
            name: Potencia maxima
